Package com.phunware.mapping.library.maps

Contains the native map related classes for MaaS Mapping SDK

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PwBuildingMapManager.PwMarkersAddedListener
    PwMarkersAddedListener is a listener listening to added markers
    PwIndoorFloorChangeLocationListener
    PwIndoorFloorChangeLocationListener is a listener listening to floor changes in the map
    PwIndoorLocationStatusListener
    PwIndoorLocationStatusListener is a listener listening to indoor location status changes.
    PwOnBuildingDataLoadedCallback
    The PwOnBuildingDataLoadedCallback interface defines a set of methods used to receive building data-loaded callbacks
    PwOnBuildingPOIDataLoadedCallback
    The PwOnBuildingPOIDataLoadedCallback interface defines a set of methods used to receive Points of Interests data-loaded callbacks
    PwOnCameraChangeListener
    The PwOnCameraChangeListener interface defines a method used to receive camera-related callbacks
    PwOnFloorChangedCallback
    The PwOnFloorChangedCallback interface defines a method used to receive floor-related callback
    PwOnMapDataLoadedCallback
    The PwOnMapDataLoadedCallback interface defines a set of methods that you can use to receive map data loaded callbacks.
    PwOnSnapToRouteCallback
    The PwOnSnapToRouteCallback interface defines a set of methods that you can use to receive "Snap to route" start and stop callbacks.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PwBuildingMapManager
    The PwBuildingMapManager provides a simple interface for fetching building data and resources.
    PwMapOverlayManagerBuilder
    PwMapOverlayManagerBuilder provides the ability to manage map overlays, and create PwBuildingMapManager objects
    PwRouteUtils
    This class provides helper functions for creating routes.
